1. Mnogih ljudi se plaši visina. (*mnogih*) (Many people are afraid of heights.)
2. *Mnogih* životinja ugrožena je zbog uništavanja staništa. (Many animals are endangered due to habitat destruction.)
3. Nema dovoljno hrane za mnoge, dok *mnogima* preostaje samo bacanje hrane. (There isn't enough food for many, while many others only have the option of throwing away food.)
4. *Mnoge* zemlje se bore sa posledicama klimatskih promena. (Many countries are struggling with the consequences of climate change.)
5. Ovaj problem pogađa *mnoge* ljude širom sveta. (This problem affects many people around the world.)
6. *Mnogi* naučnici tvrde da je vakcina efikasna. (Many scientists claim that the vaccine is effective.)
7. Da bi postigli uspeh, *mnogi* ljudi moraju da naporno rade. (In order to achieve success, many people have to work hard.)
8. *Mnogima* je potrebna pomoć u ovim teškim vremenima. (Many people need help in these difficult times.)
9. Ovaj grad ima *mnogo* restorana koji nude internacionalnu kuhinju. (This city has many restaurants that offer international cuisine.)
10. *Mnogo* ljudi ne razumeju važnost recikliranja. (Many people do not understand the importance of recycling.)